  <brief_title>Pin Site Infection Prevention for Open Tibial Fracture</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Silversulfadiazine Prevent Pin-site Infection in Open Tibial Fracture?: A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
